    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chips are cooking, peel and slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced shallot</strong> and <strong>ground cumin</strong> and cook for 1-2 min</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
