        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>meat-free mince</strong> to the pan and cook for 3-4 min further, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p><p>Tip: Try not to stir too often so the mince gets nice and brown!</p><p>Meanwhile, dissolve your<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong> in 250ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[325ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [400ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add your<strong> tomato paste</strong>, <strong>chipotle paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong>, then mix to combine – this is your<strong> spicy stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1599212072064-x200.jpg",
