      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chilli is cooking, combine your <strong>mayo </strong>with the zest and juice of half your <strong>lime[s]</strong>, 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> [2 tbsp]</span> <strong>water</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>in a bowl – this is your <strong>zesty slaw dressing</strong></p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
