    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail, peel and grate your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper<strong> </strong>and shred finely</p><p>Combine the <strong>grated carrot</strong>, <strong>shredded lettuce</strong> and <strong>zesty slaw dressing</strong> then give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>zesty slaw</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lime</strong> into wedges</p>",
